               <p>these to Mr. Beeby;" and he gave me 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6 1/2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>—he said, "Have you got any halfpence?"—I said, "No"—he said, "I must owe you one"—he had to give me 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 7<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—he only gave me 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6 1/2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>—the other tickets, and this, and the 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 7<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., make up the 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.,—I did not reck on it up myself.</p>
